g rates every 8 hours at 00:00, 08:00, and 16:00 UTC using a time-weighted average of the premium between perpetual and mark prices. The funding rate typically ranges from -0.375% to +0.375% per 8-hour period, with extreme spikes during meme coin frenzies. Bybit's unified trading account allows seamless margin management across spot and derivatives positions for delta-neutral strategies."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
